A deep depression over the south-west Bay of Bengal has intensified into cyclonic storm Burevi in in.
Heavy rains lash T.N., Puducherry as cyclonic storm Burevi nears.
According to the India Meteorological Department ‘Burevi’ lays centred over north Sri Lanka and adjoining
Gulf of Mannar, and 310 km east-northeast of Kanniyakumari.

